      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, \"warehouse elves\" and \"goblins\"? I'm not sure what you mean by that. I'm looking for actual logistical or technical causes like shrinkage or unit of measure errors. Can you stick to the professional analysis? What are the most likely non-whimsical reasons for these specific gaps?",
